00:41:03.160 --> 00:41:08.550
A home is a loving place
you make for yourself.

00:41:08.550 --> 00:41:12.760
And it doesn't qualify as home if
its keys are with someone else.

00:41:12.760 --> 00:41:14.060
It doesn't qualify as home

00:41:14.060 --> 00:41:16.790
if closing its doors means
imprisonment instead of freedom.

00:41:16.790 --> 00:41:18.530
Keys will not give you a home but
Arabic poetry becomes your home

00:41:18.530 --> 00:41:19.830
when you have nowhere else to go.

00:41:19.830 --> 00:41:21.130
Never tell an Arab poet not to
write because you cannot take

00:41:21.130 --> 00:41:22.490
